rComments: I have taken this class back in Winter 2020. I have to say Professor Abdelkader is one of the best professors I've had at uOttawa. He wants the best for his students, and does everything he could to help them. He's very knowledgable of the material that was discussed in class, so don't skip any of his classes. I highly recommend him.
Clearly passionate about the material he teaches which transfers to his lectures
